metadata.name: BEEBLE BABY #1
metadata.description: BEEBLE WORLD” is the first large-scale AI social experiment where generative humans live on the blockchain, aging, working, and dying for you. The experiment immerses participants in a ‘real’ society where everyone plays a role. Councils will form. Cliques will emerge. Empires will be rise and fall. The first generation of BEEBLE BABIES will define the society for all future generations.
